    <detaileddescription>
<para>Complete graph description: nodes and entry point. Sent inside CreateAgentRequest.</para>
<para>Protocol v2: wiring lives on each node&apos;s typed <ref refid="class_u_tryll_node_params_base" kindref="compound">UTryllNodeParamsBase</ref> in fields marked with <computeroutput>meta=(GetOptions="GetExitTargetOptions")</computeroutput> (one per declared exit). Empty value = END (turn finishes after the node). There is no separate Routes list. </para>
